idence level of the forecast', example: 0.95 }),\\n  trend: z.string().openapi({ description: 'Directional trend of the spend', example: 'increasing' })\\n}).openapi({ description: 'Future spend projections' });\\n\\nexport const BillingDashboardResponseSchema = z.object({\\n  billing_summary: BillingSummarySchema,\\n  service_breakdown: z.array(ServiceCostSchema).openapi({ description: 'List of costs categorized by service' }),\\n  forecast: ForecastSchema\\n}).openapi({ title: 'Cloud Billing Dashboard', description: 'Comprehensive cloud infrastructure billing and forecast data' });\"\n}"
